Class HttpHeader

java.lang.Object
http.server.modules.header.HttpHeader
Direct Known Subclasses:
ResponseHttpHeader
public class HttpHeader extends Object
Basic and incomplete representation of an HTTP Header. Basic process for the basic functionalities implemented in this webserver.
